   1. Material Transmitted:

   WSOM Chapter E-01, Hydrologic Service Program.

   2. Summary:

   This updated chapter is essentially the same as the previous version,
   but it incorporates a clearer description of the objectives,
   management, and design of the hydrology program of the National Weather
   Service.

   3. Effect on Other Instructions:

   Supersedes WSOM Chapter E-01, Hydrologic Service Program, Issuance
   80-6, dated June 10, 1980.


